      ** Screen input fields
     D DDSDAT          S              6A
     D DDDLNO          S              6A
     D WWDLNO          S              6  0
     D BJDFIN          S              1A
     D BJRDNB          S              5P 0

      ** Working Variables
     D PErrorFlag      S              1A
     D DDFIND          S              1A
     D DDFCOD          S              2A
     D WWFCOD          S              2A

      ** Ok indicators
     D PDaySDAT        S              5P 0
